Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:32.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be still, Straw Hat Luffy's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to provide you with a voice and body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you may live as a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget all of your past relations\Nand become my obedient soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time! Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise from 500 years of slumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How truly overawing!\NHe's a piece of art! A real devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This freak... is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to say your last farewells?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is going to marry me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm disappearing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami vanished with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Belief Worth Begging to Live For!!\NBrook Defends His Afro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You refuse to quit even\Nafter I flung you outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I will continue to\Ncome back until you return to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All cower at the mere mention\Nof the swordsman Ryuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! You are my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bodies are worlds apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will come back to me!\NYou belong under my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Humming Swordsman isn't the\Nonly one here who knows our secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rottin' bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't die" is like our secret code.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna live in fear of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that after a person loses his shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he gets taken down this long staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Luffy got carried this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were chasing after him when Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Nami is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he wants to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save her when we come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the more reason to hurry to Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wake up Straw Hat and the\Nguys and recover their shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the island is infested\Nwith zombies. That won't be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of zombies,\Nhow did you take them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That skeleton taught us how. We used this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, guys, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?\N--The zombies' weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how effective it was in my\Nbattle against this spider monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their weakness? What exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies have a weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can purify them if we\Nstuff salt into their mouths, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:08:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what exactly was that\Nmonstrous roar that came from upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! We followed that sound here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Luffy's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you all about what we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, we're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it coming! He still wants more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does a Special Zombie eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to consume\Neverything on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really stuffs his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumacy, why were you\Nharboring the pirates? Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk! You're so not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mini-Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been feeding me and I\Ndon't even know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course, the quantity bites and the food's nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it, Special Zombie!\NDon't step out of bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think gifted us\Nwith the ability to move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so rude to the ruler\Nof Thriller Bark if I were you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday the master is going\Nto become the King of the--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry! He told me to say all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude! Don't sell a friend out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry! I want more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's gobbled up nearly\Nall of the food on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're storing food in the\Ntreasure room in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to serve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Cindry-chan!\NAlways prepared for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Great!\N--I'm impressed that you set\Naside emergency rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But if you give that to Oars,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it defeats the point of the emergency rations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we completely run out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not nice, Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyoro, Nin, Bao! Run over to\NHogback's mansion and get the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on it, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lend a helping hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let those pirates find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for the Humming Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If these guys could remove\Nthe spider monkey's shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're super bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the pirates?! The Humming Swordsman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I dropped this,\Nbut here it is! It's the basement key.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This leads to the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haul the stuff back up--all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feed him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This batch is actually pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A salted fish is somewhere in that pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he eats it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's salted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Special Zombie eats that, its shadow will--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, the master\Nis going to let us have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find it before he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish... Where is the fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Perona-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! Don't say anything, Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish! Fish! Fish! Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fish looks mighty yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't think you'll find it to\Nyour liking, Special Zombie-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sort of thing I\Nhave to find out for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Do you want\Nto get eaten along with the fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, don't let him eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you guys getting\Nbetween me and my fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-We thought this might taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dried meat! Yeah, it's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving after all that hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll help myself to some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh! Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Oars! Five hundred years ago,\Nyou left behind countless legends
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as an infamous villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just now, I resurrected you in\Nmodern times to serve as my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Subordinate"? Forget it! I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a zombie like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is cramped and boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll set sail and travel\Nonce around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A voyage around the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This special freezer is encased in\Na super thick wall made of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't put a dent in--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rottin' bad! Oars has gone outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I could have\Nsworn my arm could stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to disgrace yourself by crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anything but my afro! Anything but my afro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you beg me to spare\Nyour life, just like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not how it will go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustered the courage to strike\Ndown those scary-looking zombies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they got right back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have some sort of weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I won't get my shadow back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I find my zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it off, zombies have\Nhorrendously scary faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the guys got purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This picky eater just had\Nto grill the fish with salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--The idiot! He must have been new.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He grilled the fish with salt...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the zombies' weakness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bastard! We stole your shadow\Nthe other day, Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which zombie did you stuff my shadow into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't answer, I'll scatter\Nfish all across the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you scatter them around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, that's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it couldn't possibly be salt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? "Salt"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-So what if you s-s-scatter that around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies really are insanely scary!\NI hate nighttime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jeez... It was just a grasshopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gave me a fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's dangerous for me to\Nbe out during daylight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it's easy for enemies to find me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it! I'll sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm scared, singing can\Nserve as a good distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful not to look at the\Nzombies' faces as I swiftly purify them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bound to run into my shadow eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that song coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's humming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal? What is\Nhappening on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He appears out of the darkness while humming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scary-looking swordsman\Nis searching for his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's wiped out practically\Nall of the Soldier Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perona-sama, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! Don't wake me up, Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last we meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so strong? Isn't this\Nzombie supposed to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up!\NAnd here we use the same style!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will end the same no matter\Nhow many times you come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like to increase\Nyour speed somewhat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall cut that troublesome afro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't! At the very least,\Nplease leave my afro alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're my shadow, why don't you\Nunderstand how important this afro is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time has stopped for my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it would never grow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it? I have forgotten\Nall about the days I served you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My current masters are\NMoria-sama and Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skeleton that treasures its afro\Nis nothing short of ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop! Anything but my afro!\NAnything but my afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but my afro!\NNot my afro! Not the 'fro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a dirty move!\NAre you not ashamed of yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you will! There is a reason\Nwhy I cannot afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are most pathetic, former master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry. I admit defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to die, it would affect me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the epitome of disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:22:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While waiting for my chance to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have spent these past five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...growing stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be ready to hold the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. We can start whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a lovely bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her dressed and bring\Nher to the ceremony hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That right? So that skeleton\Nhelped you out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That punk said he's endured these past\Nfifty years to keep a promise with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whale friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A whale...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Man's Promise Never Dies!!\NTo the Friend Waiting Under the Distant Sky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
